Set Up Segment Intelligence

Setting up Segment Intelligence involves several steps that you complete sequentially. The setup page guides you through the process of connecting first and third-party data and indicates which steps are required. To get the most comprehensive view of your data, also complete the recommended steps.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience	Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions


USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To manage Data Cloud:	Data Cloud Admin permission set
To set up Segment Intelligence:	Data Cloud Admin permission set
IMPORTANT Before integrating your Marketing Cloud data with Data Cloud, you must set your Marketing Cloud user default business unit to the Enterprise ID. Data Cloud supports only Marketing Cloud Enterprise 2.0 account connections.
From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Segment Intel, and then select Segment Intel Setup.
As you progress through the Segment Intelligence setup steps, refresh the page to view the completed steps. Completed steps are marked with a green check mark.

For deeper insights into your data, in addition to the required steps, also complete the recommended steps.
